00:24:47.050 --> 00:24:48.120
to change the status quo.

00:24:48.120 --> 00:24:50.171
MARTHA ORTIZ: Of course.

00:24:50.171 --> 00:24:51.670
SPEAKER: There's
one anecdote that I

00:24:51.670 --> 00:24:55.090
would like to share with the
audience that illustrates

00:24:55.090 --> 00:25:01.480
