Imagine my husband was working
with the current president,

00:32:45.380 --> 00:32:48.760
and I say I cannot
sit with these people.

00:32:48.760 --> 00:32:49.260
I must go.

00:32:49.260 --> 00:32:50.190
SPEAKER: Of course.

00:32:50.190 --> 00:32:52.320
MARTHA ORTIZ: I cannot
be in the same table.

00:32:52.320 --> 00:32:55.020
I have another idea of life.

00:32:55.020 --> 00:32:56.900
I have values.

00:32:59.770 --> 00:33:02.470
So go for your work.

00:33:02.470 --> 00:33:04.370
I will stay here.

00:33:04.370 --> 00:33:08.120
SPEAKER: And congratulations,
you have actually stayed.

00:33:08.120 --> 00:33:09.370
MARTHA ORTIZ: But it was hard.

00:33:09.370 --> 00:33:11.617
SPEAKER: And stayed
for the long time.

00:33:11.617 --> 00:33:12.700
MARTHA ORTIZ: It was hard.

