But you find the strength.

00:33:19.260 --> 00:33:20.440
You find the strength.

00:33:20.440 --> 00:33:24.880
SPEAKER: And now, Martha, with
your most recent venture--

00:33:24.880 --> 00:33:25.690
MARTHA ORTIZ: Yes.

