we need to venture
elsewhere, and we often

00:33:53.020 --> 00:33:57.250
struggle, no, on how to
adapt to that new market.

00:33:57.250 --> 00:33:59.260
And you have that
added complexity

00:33:59.260 --> 00:34:03.880
that you have said that
you want to bring and stay

00:34:03.880 --> 00:34:05.260
as authentic as possible.

00:34:05.260 --> 00:34:06.310
MARTHA ORTIZ: Of course.

00:34:06.310 --> 00:34:12.230
SPEAKER: How do you
balance that objective

00:34:12.230 --> 00:34:13.940
of being-- like
remaining as authentic

00:34:13.940 --> 00:34:19.850
